-- =============================================================================
-- QUID COMPANY TERMINAL
-- CompanyTerminal
--
-- Company registration + company control terminal in one program.
--
-- Keeps the original registrar flow, then adds:
--   * Load/control one active company owned by the logged-in citizen
--   * View company account details / balance / shareholders
--   * Capitalise company from the logged-in citizen bank account
--   * Pay company funds back out to the registered owner citizen account
--   * Connect to ContractServer
--   * Post company contracts
--   * View contracts involving the active company
--   * Mark claimed contract fulfilled
--   * Cancel company-posted contract
--
-- Notes:
--   * Company payouts require ServerSideAccounts_COMPANY_WITHDRAW or any bank server
--     build with the company_withdraw handler installed.
--   * Pay-ins still use the normal citizen transfer handler.
--   * Contract posting currently does not lock escrow because ContractServer
--     payment hooks are not implemented yet.
-- =============================================================================

